spec_data.Name: perl-DBIx-RunSQL
spec_data.Description:
This module abstracts away the "run these SQL statements to set up
a database" into a module. It also abstracts away the reading of
SQL from a file and allows for various command line parameters
to be passed in.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 10:03:21 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Run SQL commands from a file
